<b><font color="#800000">Install MS-MPI</font></b>

<ol>
<li>
Download
Microsoft MPI, MS-MPI,
(HPC Pack 2012 R2 MS-MPI Redistributable Package) from
<a href="http://http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/" target="_blank">
Microsoft Developer Network</a>
or
<a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/bb524831%28v=vs.85%29.aspx" target="_blank">
here</a>;
<br>
<img src="./figures/msmpi_1.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on the saved files to start installation.
<font color="red">The installation requires "Administrator" privilege.</font>
Click 'Next' to continue.
<br>
<img src="./figures/msmpi_2.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Check ``I accept the terms in the License Agreement'' and then click 'Next'
to continue.
<br>
<img src="./figures/msmpi_3.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Use default folder to install. Click on the 'Next' button.
<br>
<img src="./figures/msmpi_4.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on the 'Install' button.
<br>
<img src="./figures/msmpi_5.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on the 'Finish' button.
<font color="red">You may need to check Windows Update.</font>
<br>
<img src="./figures/msmpi_6.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

</ol>
